        "summary": "Isaiah speaks about the Messiah\u2014The Messiah will have the Spirit, preach the gospel, and proclaim liberty\u2014In the last days, the Lord will call His ministers and make an everlasting covenant with the people.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
